fields.title: Black Panther 2
fields.review: This Wakanda Forever is outstanding. It handles loss, grief and revenge with a maturity and seriousness rarely seen in the MCU. Black Panther continues to be their crown jewel. Letitia Wright, Angela Bassett and Tenoch Huerta all bring some of the best acting I've seen all year.

fields.title: Ashiap Man
fields.review: This is a terrible movie. It's a mess of a story, the acting is terrible and the CGI is laughable. I can't believe they made a sequel to this.

fields.title: Avengers Endgame
fields.review: Exciting, entertaining, and emotionally impactful, Avengers: Endgame does whatever it takes to deliver a satisfying finale to Marvel's epic Infinity Saga.

fields.title: Doraemon the Movie: Nobita's Treasure Island
fields.review: Doraemon the Movie: Nobita's Treasure Island is a fun adventure that will keep you entertained for the entire runtime. It's a great movie for the whole family.

fields.title: Pengabdi Setan 2
fields.review: Pengabdi Setan 2 is a Scary movie that will keep you entertained for the entire runtime. It's a great movie for the whole family.

fields.title: Dear Nathan
fields.review: Dear Nathan is a fun adventure that will keep you entertained for the entire runtime. It's a great movie for the whole family.

fields.title: Top Gun: Maverick
fields.review: Top Gun: Maverick pulls off a feat even trickier than a 4G inverted dive, delivering a long-belated sequel that surpasses its predecessor in wildly entertaining style.

fields.title: Doctor Strange in the Multiverse of Madness
fields.review: Doctor Strange in the Multiverse of Madness delivers all the action and visual excitement you want in a Marvel movie while taking the franchise in a much darker direction.

fields.title: Morbius
fields.review: Cursed with uninspired effects, rote performances, and a borderline nonsensical story, this dreary mess is a vein attempt to make Morbius happen.

fields.title: The Batman
fields.review: It's long, but The Batman looks and sounds great, and its grounded take on Gotham is a solid fit for this Caped Crusader.
